data.description: Welcome to your new home in the beautiful gated community of Walker Estates in Donna, TX! This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is perfect for anyone seeking a peaceful, comfortable living space. With a spacious backyard of 10,636 square feet, you'll have plenty of room to relax and enjoy the outdoors. The community is conveniently located just one block from FM 493 and south of the expressway, making it easy to get around town. Don't miss the opportunity to make this excellent value home yours!
